Hello the program doesnt care after line 3 so im just gonna write my comments here.
name is characters name
keywords is the keywords. Seperate them with ',' and CHARACTERNAME = the character name entered in 'name=' and SKINNAME is the skin's name when you input it.
skintag is the shortened version of the characters name. the thing that comes after 'Skin{SKINTAG} BLABLABAL InvIcon.png'